Class ReadKeyFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • ReadKeyFile
  • public class ReadKeyFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an object that contains all necessary things from the key file. The objects created by this class are constructed with with a key text file and uses that to get the key array, starting key, and length
    Author:
    Dean Farwell
